{"tid":359948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普點名譴責極右分子「罪犯」","createTime":"2017-08-15T01:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T04:26:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"844788bb703d50683a02b673e38f59853ae950ee","tid":359948,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57081781&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57081781%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170815&d=5r9K3LpCLxi7ws6UocUQQdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=ef86c09f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57081781%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170815&h=ed32185f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57081781&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170815</a><br />\n<br />\n【兇殘撞人】特朗普向壓力屈服 點名譴責極右分子「罪犯」<br />\n即時國際 <br />\n2017-08-15 01:21:32 HKT<br />\n<br />\n美國維珍尼亞州上周六極右集會爆發嚴重暴力事件後，總統特朗普因沒有明確譴責白人至上主義而受到指摘。面對各方壓力，他周一終於點名譴責3K黨等仇恨團體。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮說：「種族主義是邪惡的，以種族主義之名作出暴力行為的人，包括3K黨、新納粹、白人至上主義分子，以及所有令人厭惡的仇恨團體，都是罪犯和暴徒，有違美國人重視的價值。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普日前回應事件時無明確指摘右翼，而只批評「多方」都顯示了仇恨、偏見和暴力，遭到包括民主共和兩黨在內的各方批評。"},{"pid":"e491485145e1b9db5a7a8438e5f95a91ac083405","tid":359948,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c516b7b1da35fc7148e28268ec8bb6cc4f65534","tid":359948,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"佢既支持者喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c8ddf71f3e6eb408e2160bed872adc26392256","tid":359948,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl